description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by internationally certified astrologer & psychotherapist Dr. Jennifer Freed to talk about her Sexual Wisdom course, as well as better ways to discuss relationships & sex with people of all ages. 

They get to the root of what psychological astrology is and how can it help you understand your relationships, the importance of defining your values and where you learned your views on sex, and true embodiment – how to really be present in your body and feel all your senses.
